{"tid":1473203,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民意例子:我阿媽近排先由中立變黃都無割","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:14:32.000Z","uid":131767,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f71abddd29e6f6aabe9cbb26958a61c1d0836a","tid":1473203,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:58:48.000Z","msg":"幫大家打吓氣<br />\n<br />\n我阿媽六月都仲係不問世事中立撚<br />\n日日都講「總知暴力就係唔啱」<br />\n<br />\n開始變黃係721<br />\n睇住成晚都無狗去元朗救市民<br />\n佢終於認清咗政府同狗都係仆街<br />\n之後新聞佢都愈睇愈嬲<br />\n<br />\n去到機場捉公安同大陸記者嗰日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>本身都驚阿媽會唔鍾意會割<br />\n點知根本無事</strong></span></span><br />\n佢話去得機場就預咗俾人打啦<br />\n無融咗佢咪算佢好彩<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話俾我聽<br />\n佢發現黑警想捉手足之後俾圍一幕<br />\n只有tvb將警察想捉手足呢個前因剪走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打咁多都係想同大家打氣<br />\n今次非完美，但可接受，一齊改善<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8abbb6c41604f81f8f81c634a9747442f63d4d4","tid":1473203,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:59:35.000Z","msg":"今次唔可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf4735d13787f6e154fc82dd2748faaa4872c80","tid":1473203,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:00:31.000Z","msg":"818見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125dc570daeba569d7bd3f08a6c79ad20bd04bdf","tid":1473203,"uid":284565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:01:16.000Z","msg":"我老母都係，平時成日話睇得新聞多個人會抑鬱，搞到佢個人又藍又黃，最近開始慢慢睇返多D 新聞，先同全家人一齊屌政府同黑警<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借推一下，大學生請入<br />\n<br />\n［第三次po 了］做問卷籌錢俾612 人道支援基金<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3852777fe846fb0441b5a641fa412d9d98e2cd72","tid":1473203,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:07:12.000Z","msg":"811 721 612"},{"pid":"2b5fa85316f308e9e0294b1c3950c4d06cb732cb","tid":1473203,"uid":153376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：我老母話無打死佢都算偷笑<br />\n<br />\n利申老母和理非"},{"pid":"d1a6582a53dc9bc9dc044aecb13d438e831bc423","tid":1473203,"uid":33215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:10:54.000Z","msg":"我媽都係<br />\n早排先話掟磚唔好<br />\n幫佢戒左cctvb之後<br />\n效果顯著 冇割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4ee93515ce122dba8c3187497b7141efcab08e","tid":1473203,"uid":164211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:13:43.000Z","msg":"Yes. 我屋企人都係 由中立變到狂屌d狗。就算睇到tvb播都狂屌d狗 屌得激動過我"},{"pid":"6e62bf1fa9819f4a5a55403377509b3350b63413","tid":1473203,"uid":33215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1a6582a53dc9bc9dc044aecb13d438e831bc423","tid":1473203,"uid":33215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:10:54.000Z","msg":"我媽都係<br />\n早排先話掟磚唔好<br />\n幫佢戒左cctvb之後<br />\n效果顯著 冇割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:15:18.000Z","msg":"琴晚番到屋企<br />\n佢話好驚心啊睇左成晚直播(rthk)<br />\n佢仲話 都唔知個人(環時)做咩諗住逃走<br />\n黎得就預左多人嫁啦<br />\n多人就預左走唔到嫁啦<br />\n真.媽媽 we connect<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08af6c358b01b51f2791f1ca4246835ee2dda992","tid":1473203,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:33:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818， 追討黑警濫權!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818， 正視警黑合作!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXPug1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXPug1n.jpg&h=448ec9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68c670730e311e6007709abbade385acc5e175d6","tid":1473203,"uid":293603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:42:48.000Z","msg":"我媽係淺黃 我今日都驚驚地佢變中立<br />\n所以我一見到佢就諗住洗佢腦<br />\n點知 佢一輪咀咁狂屌 <br />\n話個死大陸仔係度搞搞震 <br />\n打佢唔撚死真係唔抵<br />\n成班仆街狗 打到d細路個個骨折<br />\n佢地絕子絕孫 就算生得出都係發瘟狗<br />\n下刪一千字 大部分粗口<br />\n跟住我就放心哂 佢已經變成深黃了 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c735fc70146604854bb37441e495154b08ff5358","tid":1473203,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769b9cc999dc8e85670d719375137a72a157b7c1","tid":1473203,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12a9da1dbbf30b30abc798f7e96306d38e1757e","tid":1473203,"uid":131767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DbQdRcW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbQdRcW.png&h=dea6492b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c0bc17fab9bd0df62d024f8a6d640fde0f47c1e","tid":1473203,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-